This directory contains code to produce PDF documents as web services.

Documents are generated from raw XML data produced by Corylus
Ruby-on-Rails part and XSL stylesheets.

Required software:

- Sun/Oracle jdk >= 1.4
- Apache Tomcat >= 5.5

These Java archives need to be installed in tomcat/common/lib:

  fop.jar (textproc/fop)
  avalon-framework.jar (devel/avalon-framework)
  batik.jar (graphics/batik)

Optional:

  jai_core.jar (Allow the use of bitmap images)
